WolfBlade::

She ran until her legs felt as if they would fall apart any second. 
She stopped once she was in visual range.  She sat just outside 
weapons range and opened her commlink.  "Hey! Anyone there? It's me? 
WolfBlade. Come on guys.  Charger? Nitro? Azuretron. Come on you 
guys. This isn't funny. Blugeron? Skywrecker? ClawDigger? Will you 
guys lower the shields and let me in. I'm beat and tired.Been running 
for two days. Oh please guys, let me in."
she sat in wolf mode looking at the base.
